title: Cotton Pant Suit - Bottle Green
body_html:
Crushing on green and how! Made in cotton, this women’s dark green pant suit is the perfect power suit for the summer! The blazer has a single hook for closure, shawl lapel and functional pockets. The trousers have a hook and zip for closure. Wear it together or separate. Pair it with a classic cream shirt and black pumps for an elegant look.


Product Details:-


Blazer:-

  • Shawl lapel
  • Single-button closure
  • Full sleeves
  • Made in cotton breathable fabric, lined with soft satin
  • Dry clean only

Trouser:-

  • Regular fit
  • Left side hook and zip
  • Two side pockets
  • Made in cotton breathable fabric
  • Easy to care/Delicate machine wash/Hand wash

    Wash & Care

    Breathable Fabric Travel Friendly Dry Clean Only

title: Cotton Twill Pant Suit - Wine Red
body_html:
“Who runs the world? Girls!”

Show em’ who’s boss in this stunning wine coloured pant suit that delivers both functionality and style. Made with cotton twill fabric and lined with soft satin, it has a jacket highlighting a notched collar and two front pockets making it a captivating choice. The essential easy work pants have a regular fit with a front hook and zip closure.

Dress up in this wine pantsuit for an utterly gorgeous look by rounding off with a pair of black leather pumps and suit up, in style!

Product Details :-

Jacket :-

  • Notched collar
  • Single-button front closure
  • Two front pockets
  • Lined with soft satin
  • Made with Cotton Twill fabric
  • Dry clean recommended

Trouser :-

  • Front hook and eye with zip closure
  • Regular fit
  • Made in cotton twill fabric
  • Wash inside out with similar colors
  • Easy to care/Hand wash/Cold machine wash
  • Color may vary slightly due to user's screen settings and resolutions

    Wash & Care :-

    Dry Clean Only

title: Double Breast Pant Suit - Royal Blue
body_html:
Prove your power in a royal blue formal pant suit that makes a statement addition to your wardrobe. The blazer features notched collars, two functional pockets and is lined with soft satin. The pants are designed for a regular fit, with loops on the waist, front hook and a zip closure. Style this royal blue trouser suit with a fitted white shirt and keep your accessories minimal with a simple pair of hoops and black court heels.

Product Details :-

Jacket :-

  • Notched collars with double breasted jacket
  • Two functional pockets in the front
  • Lined with soft satin

Trouser :-

  • Front hook and eye with zip closure
  • Loops on the waist
  • Two side pockets
  • Regular fit

Fabric and Care :-

  • Made in Poly Viscose fabric; soft to skin and less prone to wrinkling
  • Dry clean only

    Wash & Care :-

    Dry Clean Only
